                            <comment id="14261277" author="joshrosen" created="Tue, 30 Dec 2014 17:32:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Removing 1.0.x and 1.1.x as affected versions, since PythonBroadcast was added in 1.2.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
